Revenue Model
GigShield operates on a weekly subscription premium model. Revenue is collected every Monday via UPI AutoPay mandate.
Revenue per worker per week  = Weekly Premium Paid
Avg. premium (blended tiers) = ₹52/week

Year 1 Target:  10,000 active workers
Weekly Revenue: 10,000 × ₹52 = ₹5,20,000
Annual Revenue: ₹5,20,000 × 52 = ₹2.70 Crore

