Reserve Management
Every week, collected premiums are allocated as follows:
Weekly Premium Collected (100%)
  ├── 40% → Disruption Payout Reserve Pool
  ├── 30% → Operational costs + platform fees
  ├── 15% → Reinsurance layer (partner insurer)
  ├── 10% → Technology & ML infrastructure
  └──  5% → Fraud buffer / disputed claims

