Regulatory Context
In India, parametric insurance for income protection falls under IRDAI's microinsurance guidelines. Key considerations:

IRDAI Microinsurance Regulations 2015: Products with sum insured ≤ ₹2L qualify for simplified underwriting
Partner Model: GigShield operates as a tech platform; insurance risk underwritten by a licensed IRDAI insurer partner
Distribution: Digital distribution via own platform — no agent commission overhead
Compliance: All premium collection via Razorpay (regulated payment gateway)


For MVP/hackathon: Razorpay sandbox mode — no actual regulatory filings required.


Break-Even Analysis
Fixed Monthly Costs (infrastructure + team): ~₹3.5L/month
Revenue per worker/month: ₹52 × 4.3 weeks = ₹223/worker/month
Net revenue per worker (after claims): ₹223 × 54% = ₹120/worker/month

Break-even workers: ₹3.5L / ₹120 = ~2,917 active workers

Realistic break-even timeline: Month 4–5 (with proper sales partnerships with platforms)

